title: Authorizes the governor to negotiate and enter into an interstate compact for the exchange of information on registered sex offenders
summary: Authorizes the governor, on behalf of the state, to negotiate and enter into an interstate compact for the exchange of information on registered sex offenders.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the executive law and the correction law, in relation to authorizing the governor to enter into compacts with other states for out-of-state sex offender registration
